description:
Norah Jones joins Anna to talk about music, teaching your kids to swear, the potential of Just Friends 2: Jones and James, puzzles, fiddles, nostalgia, the wink that changed Norah’s life, Keanu Reeves, Cyndi Lauper, Bob Marley and more. Later in the episode Anna is joined by dating expert, coach, matchmaker and creator of LEVEL Connections, April Beyer to offer some practical advice on how to connect even during these unusual times.
